---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Casey Irvine — Software Engineer, builder, and content creator.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">About</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>
        Hey, I'm Casey. I'm a software engineer who's been building things at Microsoft
        and tinkering with developer tools, AI workflows, and whatever catches my attention.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is where I share what I'm learning — through blog posts and
        <a href="/videos">short-form videos</a>. Topics range from AI-assisted development
        to extensions, DevOps, and the occasional deep dive into something I probably
        shouldn't have rabbit-holed on.
      </p>
      <p>
        I believe in learning in public, building useful things, and not taking
        myself too seriously. Hence the tagline.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Find me elsewhere</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/cirvine-MSFT">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://youtube.com/@CaseyIrvine">YouTube</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
